data.description: This home is located in Kings Gate and is in walking distance to the Chase A Guy Park. This lovely 4 bedroom home or 3 bedroom home with a bonus room with access to the backyard also has a bonus room for an office. Large spacious living room with Coffered Ceiling, wainscoting, fireplace, built-ins and opens up to the dining room. Two eating areas with the kitchen in the middle for your convenience. White granite counter tops, recessed lighting, white painted cabinets, black appliances, double ovens, gas stove top, microwave, island and breakfast bar make this an awesome kitchen for any occasion. Isolated master with granite counter tops, double sinks plus makeup counter, separate tub and shower and walk in closet. Room could be office or nursery off the master. The other 3 bedrooms are great size and 2 share a Hollywood bath with separate sinks and toilets. Half bathroom of the kitchen will serve for living room. 3rd car garage is separate that could make a great shop. Assumable 2.99%
